---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="For Gas Station Operators — Buy, Sell, Scale | STAX Real Estate" description="Grow your gas station portfolio with a broker who has run the business. Whether you are going from 1 station to 5 or repositioning to exit, STAX knows what a good deal looks like.">

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="pt-[140px] pb-[80px] px-6 lg:px-12">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center">
      <div>
        <span class="inline-block text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[2px] uppercase text-red bg-red-light px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded mb-5">
          For Operators
        </span>
        <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl lg:text-[52px] leading-[1.12] font-semibold text-black mb-6 tracking-tight">
          Buy, Sell, or Scale — With a Broker Who's Done All Three.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700 mb-9 max-w-[520px]">
          Whether you're going from 1 station to 5, repositioning to exit, or looking for your next acquisition — we help operators make smart moves. As former CEO of a dozen-location operating company, we've overseen every P&L, handled the environmental DD, and negotiated the brand contracts. We know this business from the executive seat.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 bg-red text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-md text-[15px] font-semibold hover:bg-red-dark transition-colors tracking-wide">
            Let's Talk Strategy
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-[18px] h-[18px]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative h-[400px] lg:h-[480px] rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-gray-100">
        <img src="/images/hero-shell-station.jpg" alt="Gas Station Operator Growth Strategy" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- THE OPERATOR-BROKER ADVANTAGE -->
  <section class="py-24 px-6 lg:px-12 bg-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto">
      <div class="text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[2px] uppercase text-red mb-4">The Operator-Broker Advantage</div>
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl lg:text-[40px] font-semibold text-black mb-5 tracking-tight leading-snug">
        We speak operator. Because we've owned the business.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-[17px] leading-relaxed text-gray-700 max-w-[640px] mb-12">
        Michael Salafia served as CEO of a multi-location gas station operating company — a dozen stations with c-stores — before building STAX. He knows every detail of the business because he ran it.
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="rounded-xl p-8 bg-white border border-black/8 hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-red-light flex items-center justify-center mb-5 text-red">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-[22px] font-semibold text-black mb-3">We Know the Numbers</h3>
          <p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-gray-700">Fuel margin, inside sales per square foot, car wash revenue, labor cost as percentage of gross — we evaluate deals with the same metrics you use to run your business.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl p-8 bg-white border border-black/8 hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-red-light flex items-center justify-center mb-5 text-red">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M7.5 21L3 16.5m0 0L7.5 12M3 16.5h13.5m0-13.5L21 7.5m0 0L16.5 12M21 7.5H7.5"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-[22px] font-semibold text-black mb-3">Buy Side & Sell Side</h3>
          <p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-gray-700">Need to sell one location and acquire three? Restructure a portfolio and exit? We handle both sides of the transaction for operators — and understand how they connect.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl p-8 bg-white border border-black/8 hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-red-light flex items-center justify-center mb-5 text-red">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-[22px] font-semibold text-black mb-3">No Middlemen</h3>
          <p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-gray-700">You work directly with the principal. No junior associates learning on your deal. No transaction coordinators who've never been inside a c-store. One person, start to finish.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICES FOR OPERATORS -->
  <section class="py-24 px-6 lg:px-12">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto">
      <div class="text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[2px] uppercase text-red mb-4">What We Do for Operators</div>
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl lg:text-[40px] font-semibold text-black mb-5 tracking-tight leading-snug">
        Whether you're buying, selling, or planning your next move
      </h2>

      <div class="space-y-8 mt-12">
        <!-- Acquisition -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center">
          <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
            <div class="h-[320px] rounded-xl bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center text-sm text-gray-500">
              [ Acquisition / Growth Image ]
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
            <div class="inline-block text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[2px] uppercase text-red bg-red-light px-3 py-1 rounded mb-4">
              Buying
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-3xl font-semibold text-black mb-5">Acquire Your Next Station</h3>
            <p class="text-[17px] leading-relaxed text-gray-700 mb-6">
              We source opportunities based on operator criteria — traffic counts, gallonage trends, brand positioning, competitive radius, staffing feasibility. The metrics that determine whether a station is a good buy for someone who's going to run it.
            </p>
            <div class="space-y-3 text-[15px] text-gray-700">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="inline-block w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-red rounded-full mt-2 shrink-0"></span>
                <span>Market-by-market opportunity sourcing</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="inline-block w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-red rounded-full mt-2 shrink-0"></span>
                <span>Operational due diligence beyond the financials</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="inline-block w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-red rounded-full mt-2 shrink-0"></span>
                <span>Brand contract and supply agreement review</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Selling / Exit -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center">
          <div class="order-1">
            <div class="inline-block text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[2px] uppercase text-red bg-red-light px-3 py-1 rounded mb-4">
              Selling
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-3xl font-semibold text-black mb-5">Exit on Your Terms</h3>
            <p class="text-[17px] leading-relaxed text-gray-700 mb-6">
              Whether the buyer is another operator, a consolidator, or a passive NNN investor chasing depreciation — we position your station for maximum value. Our dual buyer network means more demand and better pricing.
            </p>
            <div class="space-y-3 text-[15px] text-gray-700">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="inline-block w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-red rounded-full mt-2 shrink-0"></span>
                <span>Operator-level valuation (not just cap rate)</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="inline-block w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-red rounded-full mt-2 shrink-0"></span>
                <span>Exposure to both operator and investor buyers</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="inline-block w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-red rounded-full mt-2 shrink-0"></span>
                <span>Tax-efficient exit structuring</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="order-2">
            <div class="h-[320px] rounded-xl bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center text-sm text-gray-500">
              [ Exit / Sale Image ]
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Portfolio Strategy -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center">
          <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
            <div class="h-[320px] rounded-xl bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center text-sm text-gray-500">
              [ Portfolio / Multi-Site Image ]
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
            <div class="inline-block text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[2px] uppercase text-red bg-red-light px-3 py-1 rounded mb-4">
              Portfolio Strategy
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-3xl font-semibold text-black mb-5">Optimize & Reposition</h3>
            <p class="text-[17px] leading-relaxed text-gray-700 mb-6">
              Multi-site operators need strategic advice. We help you identify which locations to keep, sell, or rebrand. Sell underperformers, acquire complementary sites, and restructure for scale.
            </p>
            <div class="space-y-3 text-[15px] text-gray-700">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="inline-block w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-red rounded-full mt-2 shrink-0"></span>
                <span>Asset-level performance analysis</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="inline-block w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-red rounded-full mt-2 shrink-0"></span>
                <span>Buy-sell-hold recommendations per location</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="inline-block w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-red rounded-full mt-2 shrink-0"></span>
                <span>Coordination across simultaneous transactions</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-black to-[#1a1a2e] py-20 px-6 lg:px-12 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-[640px] mx-auto">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Let's talk about your stations.</h2>
      <p class="text-[17px] leading-relaxed text-white/60 mb-8">Whether you're buying, selling, or figuring out what's next — we've sat in your chair. Free confidential consultation.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 bg-red text-white px-9 py-4 rounded-md text-[15px] font-semibold hover:bg-red-dark transition-colors">
        Schedule Your Call
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-[18px] h-[18px]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
